node.text:
Describe this home in ONE word! 😍

The House in Moscow is an upcoming 320 sqm. modern home with a pitched roof creating a spacious double height living area. The interior is kept in dark tones with wooden elements breaking the cold and adding some contrasts.

The house is designed and visualized by @stephents3d and will soon be built outside Moscow in Russia.
